  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/6bf175190bc657a5c35002799dd42d66.avif?t=1758895274\" width=613 height=317 /></span><br><br>Fight against the highly armed army of anti-magic frogs and restore peace in the forest before it's destroyed! \"Machick\" is a casual game that offers a unique experience where you are the last hope. Using ancient crafting and materials acquired from the wizardry shop, build amazing magic wands with various effects and powers. During the combat phase, face hordes of enemies, accumulate experience, and choose strategic upgrades to progress further in the challenging journey and gather resources to get even closer to your goal.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/d724cdb4246cd281bea66b64806a63e5.poster.avif?t=1758895274\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/d724cdb4246cd281bea66b64806a63e5.webm?t=1758895274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/d724cdb4246cd281bea66b64806a63e5.mp4?t=1758895274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/4b1fc6b62e424c89209a099dc0e1d05e.webp?t=1758895274\" width=613 height=50 /></span><br>- Players shape their journey by constructing their wand with items acquired in the store.<br>- Strategically choose wand components to optimize performance during combat.<br>- Puzzle challenges that test the player's creativity in crafting magical wands.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/0de8b812b27d31c42fe3d046542ec4f7.poster.avif?t=1758895274\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/0de8b812b27d31c42fe3d046542ec4f7.webm?t=1758895274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/0de8b812b27d31c42fe3d046542ec4f7.mp4?t=1758895274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/8864905eb427a433f7cf56ff9bcdaf54.webp?t=1758895274\" width=613 height=50 /></span><br><br>- Confront the army of anti-magic toads in epic and challenging battles.<br>- Employ your newly crafted wands to defeat enemies and advance the storyline.<br>- Develop unique combat skills as you progress, facing increasingly formidable creatures.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/ef499b32bcd0505d3c0f8b47a3389a27.webp?t=1758895274\" width=613 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/e105f312be3b189be5e475eb4994ad55.poster.avif?t=1758895274\" width=613 height=319 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/e105f312be3b189be5e475eb4994ad55.webm?t=1758895274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/6bf175190bc657a5c35002799dd42d66.avif?t=1758895274\" width=613 height=317 /></span><br><br>Fight against the highly armed army of anti-magic frogs and restore peace in the forest before it's destroyed! \"Machick\" is a casual game that offers a unique experience where you are the last hope. Using ancient crafting and materials acquired from the wizardry shop, build amazing magic wands with various effects and powers. During the combat phase, face hordes of enemies, accumulate experience, and choose strategic upgrades to progress further in the challenging journey and gather resources to get even closer to your goal.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/d724cdb4246cd281bea66b64806a63e5.poster.avif?t=1758895274\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/d724cdb4246cd281bea66b64806a63e5.webm?t=1758895274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/d724cdb4246cd281bea66b64806a63e5.mp4?t=1758895274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2811200/extras/4b1fc6b62e424c89209a099dc0e1d05e.webp?t=1758895274\" width=613 height=50 /></span><br>- Players shape their journey by constructing their wand with items acquired in the store.<br>- Strategically choose wand components to optimize performance during combat.<br>- Puzzle challenges that test the player's creativity in crafting magical wands.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https: